        <item>
            <title>Sigma BF 全片幅无反相机正式亮相，铝合金一体成型外壳、支援 6K 录影 + L-Log</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/24/sigma-bf-full-frame-mirrorless/dc/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=sigma-bf-full-frame-mirrorless</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/24/sigma-bf-full-frame-mirrorless/dc/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 05:59:16 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[数码相机]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Sigma]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Sigma BF]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1293659</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Sigma 发表全新 BF 全片幅无反相机，以极简设计为核心，融合 2,460 万像素感光元件、内置 230GB 储存空间和 6K 录影功能，为摄影师带来回归本源的纯粹体验。机身采用铝合金一体成型，由单块铝材经过长达 7 小时精雕细琢，造就坚固耐用的机壳。Sigma 冀望透过简约的操作介面及触觉反馈系统，让使用者在拍摄过程中得心应手、游刃有余。BF 将于 2025 年 4 月正式发售，备有黑色与银色两种机身颜色选择，建议售价为 1,999 美元（约港币 HK$15,600）。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293661" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/bf_lab_01-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/bf_lab_01-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/bf_lab_01-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.sigma-global.com/en/cameras/bf/">Sigma Global</a></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293669" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sigma_desktop_bf_003-657x580.jpeg" alt="" width="657" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sigma_desktop_bf_003-657x580.jpeg 657w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sigma_desktop_bf_003.jpeg 800w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 657px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲机身采用铝合金一体成型，图片来源：<a href="https://www.sigma-global.com/en/cameras/bf/">Sigma Global</a></p><p>BF 配备 2,460 万像素全片幅背照式 CMOS 感光元件，提供高解析度及宽广动态范围，让影像细节尽收眼底。自动对焦系统结合相位检测与对比检测技术，支援人像与动物主体追踪，即使面对瞬息万变的拍摄场景，亦能迅速对焦，捕捉精彩刹那。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293675" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/bf_product_b_02-694x448.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="448" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/bf_product_b_02-694x448.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/bf_product_b_02.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.sigma-global.com/en/cameras/bf/">Sigma Global</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293676" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/bf_product_s_02-694x448.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="448" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/bf_product_s_02-694x448.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/bf_product_s_02.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.sigma-global.com/en/cameras/bf/">Sigma Global</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293660" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/bf_camera_01-694x464.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="464" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/bf_camera_01-694x464.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/bf_camera_01.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.sigma-global.com/en/cameras/bf/">Sigma Global</a></p><p>影片拍摄方面，BF 可录制 6K 高画质影片，并支援 L-Log 设定，满足专业用户在后期调色上的需求，无论用于纪录片创作或商业摄影，皆能表现出色。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293670" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ola_thumbnail-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ola_thumbnail-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ola_thumbnail-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.sigma-global.com/en/cameras/bf/">Sigma Global</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293671" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/bf_color_standard-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/bf_color_standard-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/bf_color_standard-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.sigma-global.com/en/cameras/bf/">Sigma Global</a></p><p>操作体验方面，BF 延续极简美学，全机仅设三个按钮、一个转盘及快门键，将复杂操作简化至最直观层面。用家可以利用轻触式荧幕调整体主要拍摄参数如快门速度、光圈、ISO 感光度、曝光补偿及色彩模式，减少繁琐步骤，让用户专注于构图与创作。BF 亦是首款在拨盘与按钮中引入触觉反馈技术的无反相机，操作时能提供恰到好处的震动回应，使拍摄体验如虎添翼。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293666" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250224122934-694x343.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="343" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250224122934-694x343.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250224122934.jpg 1218w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.sigma-global.com/en/cameras/bf/">Sigma Global</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293667" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sigmabfcameraradical-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sigmabfcameraradical-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sigmabfcameraradical.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=utkFqcOnKsI&amp;ab_channel=SIGMAAmerica">Sigma America@Youtube</a><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293662" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/bf_product_b_04-694x448.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="448" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/bf_product_b_04-694x448.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/bf_product_b_04.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.sigma-global.com/en/cameras/bf/">Sigma Global</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293663" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/bf_product_s_04-694x448.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="448" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/bf_product_s_04-694x448.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/bf_product_s_04.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.sigma-global.com/en/cameras/bf/">Sigma Global</a></p><p>储存能力同样令人称道。BF 具有 230GB 储存空间，足以储存逾 14,000 张 JPEG 图片、4,300 张未压缩 RAW 图片或约 2.5 小时最高画质影片。用家可以利用 USB-C 接口充电、传输资料，无论是户外拍摄或日常应用，皆方便快捷，让创作过程无后顾之忧。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293664" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/bf_product_b_05-674x580.jpg" alt="" width="674" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/bf_product_b_05-674x580.jpg 674w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/bf_product_b_05.jpg 1045w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 674px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.sigma-global.com/en/cameras/bf/">Sigma Global</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293665" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/bf_product_s_07-674x580.jpg" alt="" width="674" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/bf_product_s_07-674x580.jpg 674w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/bf_product_s_07.jpg 1045w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 674px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.sigma-global.com/en/cameras/bf/">Sigma Global</a></p><p>图片、资料来源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=utkFqcOnKsI">Sigma America@YouTube</a>、<a href="https://www.sigma-global.com/en/cameras/bf/">Sigma Global</a>、<a href="https://petapixel.com/2025/02/23/the-sigma-bf-is-a-radically-simple-24-6mp-full-frame-compact-camera/">Peta Pixel</a>、<a href="https://www.dpreview.com/news/1398165547/sigma-bf-a-mirrorless-camera-unlike-anything-you-ve-seen">DP Review</a></p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 倾倾科技背后黑暗事</p><p>========</p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/02/24/sigma-bf-full-frame-mirrorless/dc/">Sigma BF 全片幅无反相机正式亮相，铝合金一体成型外壳、支援 6K 录影 + L-Log</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
